  "title": "StepStone Real Estate 2025 US Research Outlook",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"node__content\"> <section class=\"detail-page-head full-width-block\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-12\"> <small>StepStone Group- <span class=\"field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden\"><time class=\"datetime\" datetime=\"2025-02-28T22:54:05+00:00\" title=\"Friday, February 28, 2025 - 22:54\">Fri, 02/28/2025 - 22:54</time></span></small><h1><span class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden\">StepStone Real Estate 2025 US Research Outlook</span></h1></div></div></div> </section> <section class=\"detail-page additional-height\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-8-lg\"><div class=\"feature-image-visability\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-banner field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default insurance-library-image\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"><div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div><div class=\"field__item\"> <img alt=\"StepStoneFeatured\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid\" data-src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-02/StepStoneFeatured_3.jpg\" height=\"422\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-02/StepStoneFeatured_3.jpg\" width=\"1004\"/></div></div> </article></div></div><div class=\"audio-player\"></div><p>We are pleased to present StepStone Real Estate’s 2025 US Research Outlook webinar which provides a brief recap of 2024 and the outlook for 2025. While we focus on US property market fundamentals, we also cover capital market trends. In the coming weeks, we will be posting similar webinar modules on the European and Asian real estate markets.</p><p></p><p><a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"https://eng2e.seismic.com/i/s7Fh8fAx8Rpcmz6Buh8L4CTfoB6___WFt8cqWtUsyvjTIVjBZoNB4Q1VXWJWZPLUSSIGNNPLUSSIGNM6BtMpPe___hh8Biq45BzJat3DPea6FIcWxDI